- Run the following code to run integration test:
flutter test integration_test/calculator_app_test.dart

- When integrationDriver is used
flutter drive \
  --driver=test_driver/integration_test.dart \
  --target=integration_test/calculator_app_test.dart

- For web:
1. Install chromedriver
2. Run:
chromedriver --port=4444
3. Run:
flutter drive \
  --driver=test_driver/integration_test.dart \
  --target=integration_test/calculator_app_test.dart \
  -d web-server


- References
